library(readxl)
X2014_TU_EV_MUN_ULM <- read_excel("2014_TU_EV_MUN_ULM.xlsx")
X2014_TU_EV_MUN_AUG <- read_excel("2014_TU_EV_MUN_AUG.xlsx")
X2014_TU_MO_MUN_ULM <- read_excel("2014_TU_MO_MUN_ULM.xlsx")
X2014_TU_MO_MUN_AUG <- read_excel("2014_TU_MO_MUN_AUG.xlsx")
library(dplyr)
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':
## 
##     filter, lag
## The following objects are masked from 'package:base':
## 
##     intersect, setdiff, setequal, union
# read
query1 <- filter(X2014_TU_EV_MUN_ULM, Nummernschild  %in% X2014_TU_EV_MUN_AUG$Nummernschild)
query2 <- filter(X2014_TU_EV_MUN_AUG, Nummernschild  %in% X2014_TU_EV_MUN_ULM$Nummernschild)
query3 <- filter(X2014_TU_MO_MUN_ULM, Nummernschild  %in% X2014_TU_MO_MUN_AUG$Nummernschild)
query4 <- filter(X2014_TU_MO_MUN_AUG, Nummernschild  %in% X2014_TU_MO_MUN_ULM$Nummernschild)
#find duplicates
duplicates1 <- query1[duplicated(query1$Nummernschild), ]
duplicates2 <- query2[duplicated(query2$Nummernschild), ]
duplicates3 <- query3[duplicated(query3$Nummernschild), ]
duplicates4 <- query4[duplicated(query4$Nummernschild), ]
#remove duplicates
query1<-query1[!(query1$Nummernschild == duplicates2$Nummernschild),]
query2<-query2[!(query2$Nummernschild == duplicates2$Nummernschild),]
#Duplicates from query 3 and 4 is removed using excel.
# Create new dataframe with number
time_difference_EV = data.frame(Nummernschild = query1$Nummernschild)
time_difference_MO = data.frame(Nummernschild = query3$Nummernschild)
# Create new dataframe with time of the day
Uhrzeit_EV= data.frame(Uhrzeit = query1$Uhrzeit)
Uhrzeit_MO= data.frame(Uhrzeit = query3$Uhrzeit)

# add new column of time diff 
time_difference_EV$time_diff <- abs(as.numeric(query1$Zeitstempel) - as.numeric(query2$Zeitstempel))
time_difference_EV$speed <- 57.2/(time_difference_EV$time_diff)*60
final_EV <-data.frame(Uhrzeit_EV,time_difference_EV)
#Outliers removal 
`%notin%` <- Negate(`%in%`)
outliers <- boxplot(final_EV$speed, plot=FALSE)$out
final_outcome_EV <- final_EV[final_EV$speed %notin% outliers,]
print(boxplot(final_outcome_EV$speed))
